        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 5 at 5:04PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 500 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking an area of heavy snow over
Bozeman Pass.

HAZARD...Heavy snow affecting Bozeman Pass on Interstate 15.

SOURCE...Radar and web cam indicated.

IMPACT...Visibility below a quarter of a mile and roadways becoming
snow covered.

The heaviest snowfall is expected near the top of Bozeman Pass on
Interstate 15.
</description>
        <instruction>Delay travel if possible until conditions improve.</instruction>
